"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strasbourg\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"authorities\", \"from\": 7301, \"to\": 7312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He was told, 'It's a beautiful city',\\\" Alauzy says.\", \"from\": 7336, \"to\": 7388, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a beautiful city\", \"from\": 7356, \"to\": 7372}, {\"ngram\": \"Alauzy\", \"from\": 7376, \"to\": 7382}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He said, 'I do not care, even if I am homeless, I have a job so I need to stay, I cannot take the risk'.\", \"from\": 7389, \"to\": 7494, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a job\", \"from\": 7445, \"to\": 7450}, {\"ngram\": \"the risk\", \"from\": 7484, \"to\": 7492}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's insane to treat people like that.\\\"\", \"from\": 7495, \"to\": 7534, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 7516, \"to\": 7522}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kwantes adds: \\\"The system of trying to dispatch people all over France is not a bad system.\", \"from\": 7536, \"to\": 7627, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7600, \"end\": 7606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999996748666109, \"rank\": 2.5994705098180196e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kwantes\", \"from\": 7536, \"to\": 7543}, {\"ngram\": \"The system\", \"from\": 7551, \"to\": 7561}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 7584, \"to\": 7590}, {\"ngram\": \"a bad system\", \"from\": 7614, \"to\": 7626}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's done in the interest of the logistics of dispatching people.\", \"from\": 7628, \"to\": 7697, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the interest\", \"from\": 7645, \"to\": 7657}, {\"ngram\": \"the logistics\", \"from\": 7661, \"to\": 7674}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 7690, \"to\": 7696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just logistics for the state.\", \"fro