"ngram\": \"11 August\", \"from\": 8412, \"to\": 8421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's magical,\\\" Alauzy laughs, \\\"because for a year they sent the people away, and just when the Games arrive they find it's possible to have a place in the region of Paris.\", \"from\": 8424, \"to\": 8596, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8590, \"end\": 8595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.472281019113853e-24, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a year\", \"from\": 8468, \"to\": 8474}, {\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 8485, \"to\": 8495}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 8516, \"to\": 8525}, {\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 8565, \"to\": 8572}, {\"ngram\": \"the region\", \"from\": 8576, \"to\": 8586}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They needed to achieve their work ... and it worked.\", \"from\": 8597, \"to\": 8649, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their work\", \"from\": 8620, \"to\": 8630}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The streets are clean in Paris.\", \"from\": 8650, \"to\": 8681, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8675, \"end\": 8680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.472281019113853e-24, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The streets\", \"from\": 8650, \"to\": 8661}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is nobody in it.\\\"\", \"from\": 8682, \"to\": 8705, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nobody\", \"from\": 8691, \"to\": 8697}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some of the encampments contained unaccompanied children who had set up along the Seine to be near the organisations in the centre of Paris that support them.\", \"from\": 8707, \"to\": 8865, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8789, \"end\": 8794, \"title\": \"h