77}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 9126, \"to\": 9138}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The gyms will soon be reclaimed for school sports classes in September.\", \"from\": 9140, \"to\": 9211, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The gyms\", \"from\": 9140, \"to\": 9148}, {\"ngram\": \"school sports classes\", \"from\": 9176, \"to\": 9197}, {\"ngram\": \"September\", \"from\": 9201, \"to\": 9210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those children will not be able to return to the encampments where they had been surviving together on the streets of Paris.\", \"from\": 9213, \"to\": 9337, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9331, \"end\": 9336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.472281019113853e-24, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Those children\", \"from\": 9213, \"to\": 9227}, {\"ngram\": \"the encampments\", \"from\": 9258, \"to\": 9273}, {\"ngram\": \"the streets\", \"from\": 9316, \"to\": 9327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They replaced a tent city with picnic tables, they replaced a tent city with a big wall of cement,\\\" says Alauzy.\", \"from\": 9339, \"to\": 9452, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tent city\", \"from\": 9354, \"to\": 9365}, {\"ngram\": \"picnic tables\", \"from\": 9371, \"to\": 9384}, {\"ngram\": \"a tent city\", \"from\": 9400, \"to\": 9411}, {\"ngram\": \"a big wall\", \"from\": 9417, \"to\": 9427}, {\"ngram\": \"cement\", \"from\": 9431, \"to\": 9437}, {\"ngram\": \"Alauzy\", \"from\": 9445, \"to\": 9451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Another tent city was replaced with a huge cement block, another with just rocks and barriers.\", \"from\": 9453, \"to\": 9548, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another tent city\", \"from\": 9454, \"to\": 9471}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge cement block\", \"from\": 9490, \"to\": 9509}, {\"ngram\": \"another\", 