 kid\", \"from\": 10073, \"to\": 10078}]}, {\"sentence\": \"*** The City of Paris declined an interview to discuss the future of the displaced children.\", \"from\": 10093, \"to\": 10186, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10110, \"end\": 10115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.472281019113853e-24, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The City\", \"from\": 10097, \"to\": 10105}, {\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 10124, \"to\": 10136}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 10148, \"to\": 10158}, {\"ngram\": \"the displaced children\", \"from\": 10162, \"to\": 10184}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It issued a statement outlining its commitments to unaccompanied minors, saying: \\\"The City of Paris never has and never will evict those it shelters.\\\"\", \"from\": 10187, \"to\": 10337, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10281, \"end\": 10286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.472281019113853e-24, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 10197, \"to\": 10208}, {\"ngram\": \"its commitments\", \"from\": 10219, \"to\": 10234}, {\"ngram\": \"unaccompanied minors\", \"from\": 10238, \"to\": 10258}, {\"ngram\": \"The City\", \"from\": 10269, \"to\": 10277}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Olympic Committee did not answer a question about whether its ethics committee has looked into the ramifications of the Games.\", \"from\": 10339, \"to\": 10483, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10343, \"end\": 10374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wiki